  "title": "Sales & Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job\nVacancy: Sales & Marketing Executive (Construction)</strong></p><p><strong>Company:</strong> <strong>SUN LIKE ENGINEERING HANDYMEN PTE. LTD.</strong><br />\n<strong>Position:</strong> Sales & Marketing Executive<br />\n<strong>Employment Type:</strong> Full-Time<br />\n<strong>Location:</strong> Singapore</p><p><strong>Job\nResponsibilities</strong></p><p>·      \nPromote\ncompany construction, renovation, and handyman services</p><p>·      \nSource new\nprojects and develop sales leads</p><p>·      \nPrepare\nquotations and proposals; follow up with clients</p><p>·      \nMaintain\nstrong relationships with existing and new customers</p><p>·      \nCoordinate\nwith project and site teams for smooth job execution</p><p>·      \nHandle\nclient enquiries and provide professional consultation</p><p>·      \nAssist\nwith marketing activities, online promotion, and site visits</p><p>·      \nAchieve\nmonthly sales targets and company objectives</p><p><strong>Job\nRequirements</strong></p><p>·      \nExperience\nin sales & marketing (construction industry preferred)</p><p>·      \nGood\ncommunication and negotiation skills</p><p>·      \nSelf-motivated,\nresponsible, and target-driven</p><p>·      \nAble to\nwork independently and as part of a team</p><p>·      \nBasic\nknowledge of construction works is an advantage</p>",
